<h2>Site Administration</h2>

<h4>Your Details:</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Full Name: <%= current_admin.full_name %></li>
  <li>Email: <%= current_admin.email %></li>
</ul>

<h4>Site Content:</h4>

<p>More to be added here, will allow changing of various page content across the site</p>

<ul>
  <% @contents.each do |content| %>
